                "invention-title": [
                    "Hair cleaning agent composition",
                    "毛发清洗剂组合物"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "Provided is a hair cleaning agent composition which has excellent coacervate-forming ability, is easy to discharge from a pump, has an appropriate viscosity for easy blistering during cleaning, and has low-temperature stability for maintaining a transparent appearance even at low temperatures. A hair cleaning agent composition containing 1-20 mass% of component (A): a surfactant represented by formula (1), 1-20 mass% of component (B): an amphoteric surfactant, 0.03-3 mass% of component (C): a cationized polymer, and 0.001-1.5 mass% of component (D): beta-alanine and/or a derivative thereof, the mass ratio ((A)/(B)) being 0.2-4, and the mass ratio ((A)/(D)) being 15-300. [Chemical Formula 1] # imgabs0 # R1CO represents an aliphatic acyl group having 8-22 carbon atoms, R2 represents a hydrogen atom or a linear alkyl group or a branched alkyl group having 1-4 carbon atoms and optionally having one hydroxyl group, and M represents an alkali metal, a 1/2 alkaline earth metal or an organic ammonium."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种毛发清洗剂组合物，其凝聚层形成能力优异，同时容易从泵喷出，具有容易在清洗时起泡的适当的粘度，且具有即使在低温时也能够维持透明的外观的低温稳定性。一种毛发清洗剂组合物，其含有1～20质量％的成分(A)：由下述式(1)表示的表面活性剂、1～20质量％的成分(B)：两性表面活性剂、0.03～3质量％的成分(C)：阳离子化聚合物、0.001～1.5质量％的成分(D)：β‑丙氨酸和/或其衍生物，质量比((A)/(B))为0.2～4，且质量比((A)/(D))为15～300。[化学式1]#imgabs0#R1CO表示碳原子数为8～22的脂肪族酰基，R2表示氢原子或者任选具有一个羟基的碳原子数为1～4的直链烷基或支链烷基，M表示碱金属、1/2碱土金属或有机铵。"
                }
            ]
